He hated evil with a passion and worshiped a  god called Toss boss. As a child his father had experimented on him, which is why the half dragon thing. Before leaving home to become an adventurer he killed his father for his transgressions. Taking from his body only a ring as a keepsake of the horrors of his childhood (ring eventually turned out to be the scholars ring, which gave him the ability to read and speak every language despite only knowing common and being unable to read).